### OS cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.Desktop.ini

### Editors/IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.code-workspace

### GameMaker Studio 2
# Exports & packages
*.yyz
*.yymps
# Build outputs (you can change these if you use custom names)
build/
output/
export/
artifacts/
# Temp/cache
temp/
cache/
*.log

# YYC intermediate (sometimes produced alongside project)
__YYC*
*.dSYM/

# Generated texture pages (if you export them)
texturecache/

### Art / binaries (keep source files tracked, but use LFS – see below)
# Don’t ignore these; they should be versioned:
# *.aseprite *.ase; *.psd; *.kra; *.blend; *.png; *.wav; *.ogg
# If you export ZIP builds:
*.zip
*.7z
*.rar

### OS-specific temp (Linux)
*~
.nfs*

